==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unclosed
<hw>Un*closed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>closed</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
separated by inclosures; open.</def> <rj><au>Clarendon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not finished; not concluded.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Madison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not closed; not sealed; open.</def>
<rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unclothe</ent>⟦br⟧
